INSTALL
App::authkeymgr

Install via cpan (recommended):

  $ tar xvzf App-authkeymgr-VERSION.tar.gz
  $ cd App-authkeymgr-VERSION
  $ cpan .

Install via CPANPLUS (cpanp):
  $ cpanp -i --verbose \
     http://eris.cobaltirc.org/dev/authkeymgr/dists/CURRENT.tgz

Install via Build.PL directly:

  $ perl Build.PL
  $ ./Build
  ## May need sudo:
  $ ./Build install

(Not root? Look into using local::lib to make life easy.)
